Title: 1920s Flapper Set
Body (HTML):
Get your dancing shoes on and get ready to dance the Charleston. This set has everything you will need to complete your 1920's Great Gatsby look.
Set includes:

Black headband with attached feathers.
Cigarette holder.
Pearl necklace.

Title: Black Fedora Gangster Hat
Body (HTML):
Get all dressed up for a 20s themed party with this black felt fedora.
A thick band of black satin ribbon gives the hat an old style mob gangster feel. Dust of your oversized suit and your look will be complete.
•    Black Felt fedora hat•    Measures 34cm x 31cm x 12cm•    One size fits most adults and teenagers
